		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sure, you could patch the sound register writes to routines that convert it to anything.  I do that for visual effects.  It's a matter of replacing STA $4xxx with JSRs to appropriate bits of code.
<br />
<br />That's a good idea, I should have done that with Squeedo.  That would be fun for editing waveforms and hearing it right away.

		

